## Feature 16: Update MainActivity to Add Journey History Navigation

**Update MainActivity.java:**

```java
// In MainActivity.java, update onCreateOptionsMenu and onOptionsItemSelected

@Override
public boolean onCreateOptionsMenu(Menu menu) {
    getMenuInflater().inflate(R.menu.menu_dashboard, menu);
    return true;
}

@Override
public boolean onOptionsItemSelected(@NonNull MenuItem item) {
    if (item.getItemId() == R.id.action_journey_history) {
        // Navigate to Journey History
        Intent intent = new Intent(this, com.trms.driver.ui.history.JourneyHistoryActivity. class);
        startActivity(intent);
        return true;
    } else if (item.getItemId() == R.id.action_end_duty) {
        showEndDutyConfirmation();
        return true;
    } else if (item.getItemId() == R.id.action_logout) {
        showLogoutConfirmation();
        return true;
    }
    return super. onOptionsItemSelected(item);
}
